<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>诗 on Even - A super concise theme for Hugo</title><link>https://yuanheng521.github.io/categories/%E8%AF%97/</link><description>Recent content in 诗 on Even - A super concise theme for Hugo</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 22:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yuanheng521.github.io/categories/%E8%AF%97/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>夜神游</title><link>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E5%A4%9C%E7%A5%9E%E6%B8%B8/</link><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 22:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E5%A4%9C%E7%A5%9E%E6%B8%B8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;​我在属于「托罗恩」的丛林中航行&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​叮咚作响的清泉赠我以甘醇&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​成簇成片的荣华赠我以芳香&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​我且将「弥莫里」的回响抛于脑后——&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​
​痛楚挟喧哗的西南风而远去&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​在皑皑的寒冰之天凝结 在炎炎的金乌之下熔解&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>旧</title><link>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E6%97%A7/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 Feb 2026 23:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E6%97%A7/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;谁怜阴云掩辉皓，人往灯火映万家。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;更际来新剪绪旧，独桨孤舟断情佳。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>哀歌</title><link>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E5%93%80%E6%AD%8C/</link><pubDate>Fri, 05 Dec 2025 23:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E5%93%80%E6%AD%8C/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;忳兮郁兮，哀兮怨兮。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;旧自满者，挫乎新兮。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;终者似遥，而亦近兮。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;目余将境，苍霾掩兮。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>